title: Men Into Space - Moon Probe Ep. 1 (1950's)
description:
The more-or-less realistic adventures of Colonel Ed McCauley, head of the American space program. He battles saboteurs, budget cuts, defective equipment and other problems in outer space.


This is a 50's program that aired weekly. This one here is the first program season 1.

If you like it I can put up more of them. If you don't really like it that's fine as well.

Check it out..
